About this item

  • Design for Ourfits: Such a Slim and soft watch which is great for outfits and your wrist; The slim 20mm band is comfortable and fits well
  • Make/Receive Calls: Connect to your smartphone via Bluetooth to make and receive calls directly from the smartwatch; With its built-in microphone and speaker, you can enjoy clear calls hands-free
  • Health Monitor: Our fitness watch can monitor your heart rate and blood oxygen levels to understand your health; It also tracks your sleep data, helping you analyze sleep quality and develop healthier habits
  • IP68 Waterproof Watch: The sports watch is designed with an IP68 waterproof rating, meaning it can be worn during hand washing, face washing, swimming, and sweaty activities without worry
  • Message Notification: Receive and display your social media notifications after connecting the watch to Bluetooth and allowing the app to make notifications; Avoid missing any important notifications
  • Personalized Watch Faces: Offer hundreads of watch faces in App, easily downloadable and usable; You can also personalize your watch face with your own photos, adding more vitality and individuality; It's not just a watch, but a fashionable accessory
  • Compatible Devices & Battery Life: Our smartwatch is compatible with iOS and Android smartphones only, not compatible with PCs, iPads, or tablets; One charge lasts 7 days of use, with standby reaching about 30 days

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
